textAfterTable: 12 Songs Biography Genre: Pop Years Active: '70s, '80s, '90s, '00s Affectionate parodies of pop music and occasional humorous cultural commentary gave the Dutch new wave band Gruppo Sportivo a cult following in the early 1980s, although much of their material was available only through import sources.
